text:
The food here was amazing and deserves 5 stars. We went there for breakfast yesterday, and I would highly recommend the Croque Madame. Great pastries as well;
The service was a catastrophe; we waited for 15 minutes after being seated to just receive a glass of water; our waitress never came to ask what we wanted to eat, nor greeted us; we received coffee that we did not ordered, and two orange juices;
I had to grab a waitress from another section in order to order our food ! Plenty of managers, but probably all of them in training.
I would go back for the quality of their cuisine, but if the service does not improve, that will be my last.
